  <div class="container">
    <h1>Contacts Adventure – Account & Data Deletion</h1>
    <p>You can request deletion of your Contacts Adventure account and all associated data at any time.</p>

    <h2>How to Delete Your Account and Data</h2>

    <p><strong>Option 1: In-App Deletion</strong></p>
    <ol>
      <li>Open the Contacts Adventure app.</li>
      <li>Go to <strong>Settings</strong> &gt; <strong>Delete Account</strong>.</li>
      <li>Follow the on-screen instructions to permanently delete your account and all data.</li>
    </ol>

    <p><strong>Option 2: Email Request</strong></p>
    <p>
      Email us at <a href="mailto:friendyhere@gmail.com">friendyhere@gmail.com</a> 
      with your registered phone number and request account/data deletion.
    </p>

    <h2>What Data is Deleted</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>All contacts you have uploaded</li>
      <li>Your account information (phone number, authentication data)</li>
      <li>All app-related data stored in our systems</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Retention Policy:</strong><br>
      Deleted accounts and data are removed immediately. For security and abuse prevention, 
      deleted users cannot re-register for 30 days.
    </p>

    <h2>What Data is Retained</h2>
    <p>None, unless required by law or for abuse prevention (e.g., a record of deletion for 30 days).</p>

    <h2>Need Help?</h2>
    <p>
      Contact us at 
      <a href="mailto:friendyhere@gmail.com">friendyhere@gmail.com</a> 
      for any questions or assistance.
    </p>
